        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice <strong>half </strong>your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Dice the <strong>remaining brown onion</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
