    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> and <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until the meat-free chick'n has lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 4,
