    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free chick'n has lightly browned, turn the heat down to<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>medium-low, add the <strong>Filipino-style tocino sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>3-4 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until the sauce has thickened to a syrup-like consistency – this is your <strong>Filipino-style sticky meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1717144051865-x200.jpg",
