            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once warmed through, push the rice to one side of the pan and crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> onto the other side</p><p>Stir the<strong> egg[s]</strong> with a wooden spoon to break the <strong>yolk[s]</strong> and cook for 1-2 min until it resembles scrambled egg, then mix it all through the rice – this is your <strong>garlicky</strong> <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
