    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Filipino-style sticky meat-free chick'n </strong>with the <strong>garlicky egg fried rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon any<strong> Filipino-style tocino sauce </strong>over the top of the<strong> </strong>meat-free<strong> </strong>chick'n</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
